social_posts.post_text: happy Joshua day to all who celebrate 🎂

DECEMBER was a good month! 
I’m coming into the new year feeling rested and ready. Big thanks to all my clients, friends, and family for your support and TLC. My goals for this year are fairly simple i just want to get my shit together and have fun 🤷🏼‍♀️ and drink more water (borrowed resolution from @cameroncancholahair)

1. The Peoples Champ - Nick looking fly as ever color by me
2. Full service salon, double shampoo by request only
3. Cheryl’s cool sock n shoe combo
4. Holiday madness/me and my assistants being spoiled rotten
5. My bomb blowout and haircut by Leila
6. Our cute lil tree
7. Watching u
8. The best Christmas gift!!! 
9. Izzy + Ozzy do Chrizzmazz
10. NYE 4EVR

JANUARY
I’m late! But i loved January. 
My girl @chelseasommers got a day on the floor (Mondays! Go see her for some bomb color),
I got to be in Hawaii with some of my absolute favorite people, and i got @thelightphone - trying to get out of the smart phone/social media infinity pool. Want to have healthy relationship with my phone like back in the day when i had MySpace but it was on the PC in my moms bedroom, not in my hand the majority of the day. Sooo here i am, logging in, from the computer in my moms room ;)
That being said, here’s another reminder that i don’t book via DM, hell i barely even check my DMs!- plz email iwantmyhaircolored@gmail.com
